               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>This manuscript contains the first of three volumes of the <title xml:lang="sa">Divyāvadāna</title>. It was consulted for the edition of the text by E. B. Cowell and R. A. Neil, but only the first few pages were collated, because they deemed it to be too similar to their other witnesses. In fact, all manuscripts of the text descend from a single 17<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>-century Nepalese manuscript (1886, vii).</p></summary>
                  
               <msItem defective="false"><title xml:lang="sa">Divyāvadāna</title><textLang mainLang="san"/><rubric xml:lang="sa"><milestone n="1v" unit="folio" facs="6"/>
